headline: General Mills Quarterly Dividend Declared
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 29, 2025--The General Mills Board of Directors has declared a quarterly dividend at the prevailing rate of $0.61 per share, payable November 3, 2025, to shareholders of record as of October 10, 2025. General Mills (NYSE: GIS) and its predecessor company have paid dividends without interruption for 127 years.
